```plantuml
@startuml Nishu0_anime_nft_marketplace
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Frontend" as FE {
}

rectangle "Ethereum/Polygon\n(Mumbai Testnet)" as Blockchain #mistyrose {
  rectangle "NFTMarketplace\nSmart Contract" as Contract #palegreen
}

rectangle "IPFS" as IPFS #aliceblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> FE

' Frontend interactions
FE <--> Blockchain : mint NFT\nlist NFT for sale\nbuy NFT\ntransfer ownership
FE <--> IPFS : upload NFT images and metadata

' Smart contract interactions
Contract --> Blockchain : execute mint, list, buy, transfer functions

' User to Blockchain interactions
User --> FE : connect wallet\nsign transactions via Metamask

@enduml
```